  "title": "Warehouse Coordinator",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Descriptions:</strong><br />Warehouse Coordinator oversees daily warehouse operations, ensuring efficient inventory control, timely order fulfilment, and compliance with safety and regulatory standards.</p><p><p>Receiving goods</p><p>Loading and unloading of goods</p><p>Price tagging of goods</p><p>Perform stocktaking and cycle count whenever required</p><p>Keep warehouse clean and tidy</p><p><br /><strong>Requirements:</strong><br />3 years of experience in logistics, warehousing, transportation, distribution, supply chain or related fields.</p></p>",
