    "description": "<p>Jobster Private Ltd<br>\nAt Jobster Private Ltd, we connect great people with great opportunities. As a trusted recruitment and manpower outsourcing partner in Singapore, we support hundreds of professionals like you across industries—from IT and engineering to finance, customer service, and beyond.<br>\nWe’re not just about placements—we’re about partnership. Your career matters to us.<br>\n<br>\nWhy Join Us<br>\nWhen you join Jobster, you don’t just get a job—you get a team behind you.<br>\n✔ Career Growth Support<br>\nWe help you build your career with meaningful roles, skill development opportunities, and guidance along the way.<br>\n✔ Quality Job Openings<br>\nWe work with reputable companies offering a wide range of roles in IT, tech support, project management, data analysis, and more.<br>\n✔ Competitive Salaries<br>\nWe advocate for you—negotiating fair, competitive salaries and making sure you’re valued for your skills.<br>\n✔ Ongoing Care<br>\nFrom onboarding to payroll, performance feedback to career advice—we’re with you throughout your journey, not just at the start.<br>\n✔ Trust &amp; Transparency<br>\nLicensed by MOM, certified in data protection, and committed to your success.<br>\n</p>",
